categories: Category:Sith Lords of the reconstituted Sith Empire

nodes.text: Darth Nacheria was a powerful female Sith Lord of the Sith Empire during the Cold War with the Galactic Republic. Prior to the Galactic War, Nacheria planned to meditate in seclusion for a decade in order to divine the Empire's future, but was convinced by the Empire to leave her armies behind for use in the coming war.
